        "body": "<p><code>com.mysql.jdbc.MysqlDataTruncation: Data truncation: Data too long for column 'item_codes' at row 1<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p>This error is coming from MySQL because whatever you're trying to persist is too large for the given field <code>item_codes<\/code>. You have several options to mitigate this<\/p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>field length on that table *<\/li>\n<li>adjust the character length in the spreadsheet<\/li>\n<li>programatically trim the length of the input.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
